I"ф<h1 id="the-marvl-task">The MaRVL Task</h1>

<p>Given <em>a pair of images</em> and <em>a caption</em>, the model needs to assign <strong>TRUE</strong>/<strong>FALSE</strong> to the example (i.e., juedge whether the caption is correctly describing the pair of images).</p>

<p>Two examples from MaRVL. The Tamil images (a) are from the concept <a href="https://ta.wikipedia.org/wiki/роПро▒рпБродро┤рпБро╡ро▓рпН">роПро▒рпБродро┤рпБро╡ро▓рпН</a> (<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jallikattu">Jallikattu</a>, part of an Indian festivity), while the Swahili images (b) are from the concept <a href="https://sw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leso">leso</a> (<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Handkerchief">Handkerchief</a>).</p>

<h2 id="example-a">Example (a)</h2>
<p><img src="/media/images/front-page-tamil.png" height="3" width="600" /> <br />
роЗро░рпБ рокроЯроЩрпНроХро│ро┐ро▓рпН роТройрпНро▒ро┐ро▓рпН роЗро░рогрпНроЯро┐ро▒рпНроХрпБроорпН роорпЗро▒рпНрокроЯрпНроЯ роороЮрпНроЪро│рпН роЪроЯрпНроЯрпИ роЕрогро┐роирпНрод ро╡рпАро░ро░рпНроХро│рпН роХро╛ро│рпИропрпИ роЕроЯроХрпНроХрпБроорпН рокрогро┐ропро┐ро▓рпН роИроЯрпБрокрпНрокроЯрпНроЯро┐ро░рпБрокрпНрокродрпИ роХро╛рогроорпБроЯро┐роХро┐ро▒родрпБ.<br />
(Translation: <em>In one of the two photos, more than two yellow-shirted players are seen engaged in bull taming.</em>)<br />
Label: <strong>TRUE</strong><br /></p>

<h2 id="example-b">Example (b)</h2>
<p><img src="/media/images/front-page-swahili-v3.png" height="3" width="600" /> <br />
Picha moja ina watu kadhaa waliovaa leso na picha nyingine ina leso bila watu. <br />
(Translation: <em>One picture contains several people wearing handkerchiefs and another picture has a handkerchief without people.</em>)<br />
Label: <strong>FALSE</strong><br /></p>

